<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4745661>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Gahrliepia mirabilis Schluger, Grochovskaja, Ngu, Hoe and Tung, 1960, lectotype. A, dorsal aspect of body; B, ventral aspect of body. Walchia delicatula (Schluger, Grochovskaja, Ngu, Hoe and Tung, 1960), lectotype. C, dorsal aspect of idiosoma; D, ventral aspect of idiosoma. Scale bars: 100 μm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4745661/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4745671>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Gahrliepia mirabilis Schluger, Grochovskaja, Ngu, Hoe and Tung, 1960. A, arrangement of dorsal idiosomal setae of paralectotype ZMMU Tdt-3227 (specimen 1); B, arrangement of ventral idiosomal setae of paralectotype ZMMU Tdt-3227 (specimen 1); C, humeral seta of lectotype; D, dorsal idiosomal seta of 1st row of lectotype; E, caudal seta of lectotype; F, preanal seta of lectotype. Scale bars: 100 μm (A, B), 20 μm (C–F)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4745671/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4745677>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Gahrliepia mirabilis Schluger, Grochovskaja, Ngu, Hoe and Tung, 1960, lectotype. A, ventral aspect of gnathosoma; B, dorsal aspect of gnathosoma; C, leg I (trochanter–tarsus); D, leg II (trochanter–tarsus); E, leg III (trochanter–tarsus). Scale bars: 20 μm (A, B), 50 μm (C–E)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4745677/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4745683>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Type specimens of Gahrliepia mirabilis Schluger, Grochovskaja, Ngu, Hoe and Tung, 1960 on slides." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4745683/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

